23#ifndef __MPFR_CVERS_H__
24#define __MPFR_CVERS_H__
25
26/* Macros to detect STDC, ICC, GCC, and GLIBC versions */
27#if defined(__STDC_VERSION__)
28# define __MPFR_STDC(version) (__STDC_VERSION__ >= (version))
29#else
30# define __MPFR_STDC(version) 0
31#endif
32
33#if defined(_WIN32)
34/* Under MS Windows (e.g. with VS2008 or VS2010), Intel's compiler doesn't
35 support/enable extensions like the ones seen under GNU/Linux.
36 https://sympa.inria.fr/sympa/arc/mpfr/2011-02/msg00032.html */
37# define __MPFR_ICC(a,b,c) 0
38#elif defined(__ICC)
39# define __MPFR_ICC(a,b,c) (__ICC >= (a)*100+(b)*10+(c))
40#elif defined(__INTEL_COMPILER)
41# define __MPFR_ICC(a,b,c) (__INTEL_COMPILER >= (a)*100+(b)*10+(c))
42#else
43# define __MPFR_ICC(a,b,c) 0
44#endif
45
46#define __MPFR_MAJMIN(a,i) (((a) << 8) | (i))
47
48#if defined(__GNUC__) && defined(__GNUC_MINOR__) && ! __MPFR_ICC(0,0,0)
49# define __MPFR_GNUC(a,i) \
50 (__MPFR_MAJMIN(__GNUC__,__GNUC_MINOR__) >= __MPFR_MAJMIN(a,i))
51#else
52# define __MPFR_GNUC(a,i) 0
53#endif
54
55#if defined(__GLIBC__) && defined(__GLIBC_MINOR__)
56# define __MPFR_GLIBC(a,i) \
57 (__MPFR_MAJMIN(__GLIBC__,__GLIBC_MINOR__) >= __MPFR_MAJMIN(a,i))
58#else
59# define __MPFR_GLIBC(a,i) 0
60#endif
61
62#endif
63
